        <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-300 space-y-1">
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-green-500 mr-2">&#10003;</span>Strong native English speaker selection</li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-green-500 mr-2">&#10003;</span>Founded 2011, well-established platform</li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-green-500 mr-2">&#10003;</span>Pay-per-lesson, no mandatory subscription</li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-green-500 mr-2">&#10003;</span>Flexible conversation-based lessons</li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-green-500 mr-2">&#10003;</span>Trial lessons available</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <a href="/reviews/verbling/" class="block w-full bg-blue-600 text-white text-center py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition font-bold">Explore Verbling</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Feature Comparison Table -->
<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 pb-8">
