    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-200 mb-2">How do Preply and Verbling compare on European tutor availability?</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Both platforms have strong European tutor networks. Preply's larger tutor base of 50,000+ includes tutors from across Europe, including Germany, Spain, France, Poland, and Italy. Verbling's 10,000+ tutors also span European countries, with particularly strong representation from Spain and Latin America.</p>
