      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-200 mb-2">Can I cancel lessons easily on both Preply and Verbling?</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Both platforms allow flexible cancellation. Preply's cancellation policy allows you to cancel lessons up to 24 hours in advance for a full refund. Verbling also offers flexible cancellation, with most tutors accepting cancellations 12 to 24 hours before the scheduled session.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-200 mb-2">Do Preply and Verbling offer trial lessons?</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm">Yes, both platforms offer trial lessons. Preply provides trial lessons at discounted rates so you can test a tutor before committing. Verbling also offers trial lessons at reduced prices. Both let you book one-off lessons without any subscription, making it easy to test multiple tutors.</p>
